      "date_time": "FIXTURE_DATE_DAY_1_TIME_9_24",
      "message": "Great question. With a traditional IRA, contributions are tax-deductible now but you pay taxes on withdrawals in retirement. With a Roth, you pay taxes now but withdrawals are tax-free.",
